## Development Rules
1. Always use Next.js App Router for new pages
2. Use CSS Modules for all component styling
3. Follow Next.js best practices and conventions
4. Use TypeScript for type safety (if applicable)
5. Maintain consistent code structure and naming conventions

## Project Structure
- Use App Router directory structure (`app/` directory)
- Components should be in appropriate directories
- Styles should be co-located with components using CSS Modules

## Environment Variables
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_DOMAIN`: API domain URL (default: https://courses-top.ru)

